# Chess Game

## About

This project is a Chess game application developed for Android. It includes features such as a fully interactive chessboard, timers for each player, and the ability to save and load games.

## Credits

The entire project, including the design and implementation of the chessboard, game logic, and user interface, was developed by Ofir Nachmany. Board pieces images obtained from WikiSpaces.com

